TITLE		Colorize listed items

OCCURRENCE	ARB_NT/Species/Search and Query/More Functions/Set color of listed species
                ARB_NT/Genome/Search and query/More Functions/Set color of listed genes
                ARB_NT/Genome/Experiment/Search and query/More Functions/Set color of listed experiments

DESCRIPTION     Sets the internal color flag ('ARB_color') of the currently listed items
                (e.g. species, genes, ...) to the selected color group, when you press the
                'Set color ...'-button.

NOTES           See LINK{color.hlp} for details about using color groups.

                Another possibility to colorize items is LINK{colorize.hlp}.

